<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.4.3">
<l>koṅkār kuḻalār kūṭiyi runtuci rittemmai</l>
<l>yeṅkō lamaiyā veṉṉiṉik kāṇpateṉ ṉātamuṉ</l>
<l>ceṅkōl valavaṉ tāṉpaṇin tētti<supplied>t</supplied>ti  kaḻumūr</l>
<l>naṅkōṉ naṟaiyūr nāmtoḻu tumeḻu neñcamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Before those with fragrance-filled curls, gathering and tittering,</l>
<l>Can say, “Sir, why still this glancing at us [and] our beauty?”</l>
<l>Arise, [my] heart! We will worship in our king’s Naṟaiyūr,</l>
<l>The city where the mighty one with a just scepter is eminent,</l>
<l rend="indent">praising [and] bowing at [the lord’s] feet.</l> 
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
